   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2045_merca_arc-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2045_merca_arc-1-a" mid="58" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Is the reason why you're trying to give me the power because of this person called Camellia?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>Please.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2045_merca_arc-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2045_merca_arc-1-b" mid="59" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Can you tell me more about her?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Arc turns gloomy.)</FONT><BR>…That's right... She's an elf who died 300 years ago.<BR>It was no one else but Goddess Vestinel who killed her...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2045_merca_arc-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2045_merca_arc-1-c" mid="60" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc${sound:npc_Arc_4786_qu_01.ogg}<BR>It would be my pleasure.<BR>No one was ever interested in my story.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2045_merca_arc-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2045_merca_arc-1-d" mid="61" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes. All elves are born from fruits of the Tree of Life.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n2045_merca_arc-1-d" mid="95" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I don't know the details but I heard that's the case.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR><FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, are the elves in Lagendia born from the Tree of Life too?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2045_merca_arc-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2045_merca_arc-1-e" mid="62" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>
Just like Mistland. That would make it easier for you to understand.<BR>I don't know about the Tree of Life in Lagendia, but for Mistland, there are rare cases of rotten and distorted fruits being borne.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2045_merca_arc-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2045_merca_arc-1-f" mid="63" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>Such fruits normally fall and rot before they hatch, but some elves are born from the fruits that have fallen.<BR>Elves born from the rotten fruit that fell on the ground are called <FONT color=#a82424>Fallen Fruit Elves</FONT> in Mistland.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2045_merca_arc-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2045_merca_arc-1-g" mid="64" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Vernicka was right.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n2045_merca_arc-1-g" mid="96" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>That's too much…….</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n2045_merca_arc-1-g" mid="97" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>No way.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>Fallen Fruit Elves are disabled from the moment they are born. In Mistland, deformities are a threat to life and a sin in itself.<BR>That's why Fallen Fruit Elves normally can't live for more than 20 years or are chased away and are neglected until they die because they are considered useless.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2045_merca_arc-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2045_merca_arc-1-h" mid="65" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Camellia</FONT> was a Fallen Fruit Elf like me. We grew on the same branch and were born on the same day.<BR>I had a distorted eye and she had shorter ears with hearing problems. We treated it as fate that we were born on the same day and we relied on each other as we survived.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2045_merca_arc-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2045_merca_arc-1-i" mid="66" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Dimension traveller…?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>But having someone to rely on doesn't mean that our lives were smooth.<BR>We thought we might die together some day. But luckily we managed to live on and when we lived for 50 years, a <FONT color=#a82424>dimension traveller</FONT> appeared before us.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2045_merca_arc-1-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2045_merca_arc-1-j" mid="67" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>"Something"?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc${action:No}<BR>That's all he told us so I don't know anything else about him.<BR>He called us <FONT color=#086171>"Children with Lagendia's Goodwill"</FONT> and said that we were born as fallen fruit elves because Mistland wanted to destroy elements from Lagendia. And he gave <FONT color=#a82424>something</FONT> to us.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2045_merca_arc-1-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2045_merca_arc-1-k" mid="68" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc${action:Talk}<BR>Something that we are about to go and find… A meteorite fragment that can awaken the power inside you.<BR>The dimension traveller called it <FONT color=#a82424>Harmonium</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2045_merca_arc-1-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2045_merca_arc-1-l" mid="69" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Arc caresses the jewel on his necklace.)</FONT><BR>With Harmonium's power, we could fix our deformities and live a longer life than other fallen fruit elves. But I still have a scar on my eye and Camellia's ears remained short.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2045_merca_arc-1-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2045_merca_arc-1-m" mid="70" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>And Camellia also attained amazing strength from Harmonium.<BR>She was a master of archery and there was nothing that escaped her arrows. She was also exceptionally better in magic compared to the other elves.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2045_merca_arc-1-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2045_merca_arc-1-n" mid="71" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>Thanks to that, she earned the praise of the other elves and eventually won the favour of Goddess Vestinel too.<BR>…<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Arc suddenly lowers his voice and looks around.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2045_merca_arc-1-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2045_merca_arc-1-o" mid="72" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>…I'm sorry but I'd like to continue with the rest of the story somewhere quiet.<BR>There are many ears in Merca's Heart.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2045_merca_arc-1-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2045_merca_arc-2" mid="73" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>Could you come and find me at <FONT color=#a82424>Cradle of the Abandoned</FONT>?<BR>There is something we need to get from that place too.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="106"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Arc appears from a building at the corner of the town which looks like a deserted house.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2045_merca_arc-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="104"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>Then I'll tell you the rest of the story at <FONT color=#086171>Cradle of the Abandoned</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-a" mid="111" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Arc appears from a building at the corner of the town which looks like a deserted house.)</FONT><BR>I'm sorry. There was something I needed to take... Shall we continue?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-b" mid="75" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>She left?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>By the time I was finally accepted to be one of the elves who managed <FONT color=#086171>Distorted Zone</FONT>, she had made a few achievements with her great strength.<BR>And soon she left me.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-c" mid="76" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>Yes. I don't know why but she always wanted to enter the <FONT color=#086171>Holy Edart Empire</FONT>.<BR>When elves are assigned a location by the goddess, we live and work there for the rest of our lives. But there is a way to enter the Empire.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-d" mid="77" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>You can either become a <FONT color=#a82424>Holy Soldier</FONT> who escorts an Oracle candidate, or become a <FONT color=#a82424>Priestess</FONT>.<BR>She said to me that she'll <FONT color=#086171>try to become a Priestess</FONT> and gave me her Harmonium before she left.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-e" mid="78" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>I didn't blame her because I thought she chose a path of devoting her life to the goddess.<BR>Camellia was a strong elf and in this world where the strong reign over the weak, such people have the right to make such choices.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-f" mid="79" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Oh no…….</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>Soon, I heard rumours that she became a Priestess.<BR>But after several decades, I found out from rumours again that she died.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-g" mid="80" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>She died in the…  experiment?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>For a long time, I thought she died honourably while serving Goddess Vestinel.<BR>But that wasn't the case. The price she paid for devoting her life to the goddess was... so vain and horrible.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-h" mid="81" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>That's right. It was an experiment to find a more powerful Oracle candidate.<BR>That experiment took place 300 years ago... The goddess wanted to know if there was a body that was more powerful than her previous vessels.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-i" mid="82" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>So the goddess ordered Childs and elves to bring women to her.<BR>Some were kidnapped and some were lured by rumours that made them come to the Empire.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-j" mid="83" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>No way…</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>She possessed the bodies of the women one by one and if the bodies were not good enough for her, she ruthlessly killed them. So many lives were sacrificed.<BR>Among them, there were little girls and old women and even Childs too.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-k" mid="84" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>…We were brainwashed that those who are strong can win the favour of the goddess.<BR>However, the goddess treated the strong ones as toys who could be sacrificed on her whim.<BR>Lives in Mistland were just tools for her…….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-l" mid="85" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc${action:Sad}{sound:npc_Arc_4786_qu_02.ogg}<BR>I didn't know anything about the cruelty and unfairness of this world that time.<BR>I only realised it when a girl was taken right before my eyes and I found out that Camellia died…….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-m" mid="86" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc${sound:npc_Arc_4786_qu_03.ogg}<BR>…That is why I devoted myself to the Anti-Goddess Faction.<BR>I want this world to fall. I want to end the world of the goddess who mercilessly killed Camellia.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-n" mid="87" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Hope? You're overrating me…</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-n" mid="101" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(I'm only doing this for my own purpose...)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc${action:Talk}<BR>And to people like me who have been abandoned by the goddess, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT> you are the only one who can make our wish come true. You are our hope.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-o" mid="88" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I guess so.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Arc smiles quietly and opens his mouth again.)</FONT><BR>Have I answered your question?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-2-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-3" mid="89" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Arc takes a pendant out and shows it to you.)</FONT><BR>This pendant was made with my Harmonium. I always carried the one Camellia gave me but I kept this one at a safe place because I didn't find a need for it.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2047_cradle_middle_arc-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="109"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>I'm planning to use this in my next plan.<BR>First, let's go back to <FONT color=#a82424>Merca's Heart</FONT>. I'll tell you more about it there.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2045_merca_arc-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2045_merca_arc-3-a" mid="108" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>$Arc$<BR>We are ready now.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
